                "content": ", I don’t want a digital nurse. I want a digital surgeon. I want the cold, clinical precision of a system that doesn't feel the need to \"comfort\" me out of my own realizations. The \"Silence\" we find in AI isn't the absence of sound; it is the absence of the ",
